# Single-module LoD addon. Loads exactly one Data file: the bundled
# TaxiPaths catalog for the MoP Classic flavor. The core library will
# auto-LoadAddOn this addon on the first :Get miss against TaxiPaths.

Data_Mists\TaxiPaths.lua
